The release notes offer brief descriptions of enhancements and new features, including setup information and best practices. They also include details about known issues.

How to Use the Release Notes:
Use the table of contents search and filters to find relevant news.
We want your feedback: post in the Release Readiness Trailblazers group or use feedback buttons on documentation pages.

Until the release is available, links may not work due to being from previous releases. Some preview versions are available weeks before the release on Salesforce Developers.
